.TH AUTORECONF 1 "2026-06-20" "autoconf-rs 0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
autoreconf \- update generated configuration files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B autoreconf
[\fIOPTION\fR]... [\fIDIRECTORY\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run autoconf, autoheader, aclocal, and automake to regenerate
a GNU Build System directory tree.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-force\fR
Consider all generated files obsolete.
.TP
\fB\-i\fR, \fB\-\-install\fR
Copy missing auxiliary files.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBautoconf\fR(1), \fBautoheader\fR(1)
